author: @adityasasmal
text: I'm getting an error at timestamp 25.28  when I'm specifying thre role and moving on to the next step. It shows error.   The error message you're encountering is related to an AWS Identity and Access Management (IAM) role ARN (Amazon Resource Name) that does not meet AWS's validation criteria. Specifically, the error indicates that the value provided for the roleArn in the CreateTrainingJob operation fails to match the required pattern. This pattern expects the ARN to point to an IAM role, not an IAM user.
